properties.property: Welcome to Astronautica Mission 0! This level will show you the basics of deep space survival. If you need a reminder of any of the skills you learn here, press (Start / Esscape) to view the guide. Don't run out of Oxygen!

(Xbox Controller / Keyboard) ____________________________________ (Left Joystick / arrow keys) -> Move (Press Left Joystick / Space Bar) -> Cancel placement (X / q) -> Hold and let go to place Drill (Y / w) -> Hold and let go use Loader and place Block (B / e) -> Use Destructor (A / r) -> Use Assembler (L / Tab) -> Toggle Loader resource to the left (R) -> Toggle Loader resource to the right (Start / Escape) -> Open Menu
